00:51:38.480 --> 00:51:39.550
How did you find me?

00:51:40.360 --> 00:51:41.440
I don't care who you are.

00:51:41.440 --> 00:51:42.880
If you're after money, go to him.

00:51:42.880 --> 00:51:43.810
It's not my debt.

00:51:44.360 --> 00:51:45.760
We're already divorced.

00:51:45.760 --> 00:51:46.760
Don't be nervous.

00:51:47.670 --> 00:51:48.800
I'm from the police.

00:51:52.280 --> 00:51:53.280
Here's my badge.

00:51:59.600 --> 00:52:00.310
[Police]

00:52:04.880 --> 00:52:06.080
Baby, wait for Mommy.

00:52:06.110 --> 00:52:07.170
I'll be right back.

00:52:13.760 --> 00:52:15.670
I want to ask you

00:52:15.800 --> 00:52:17.400
about your father, Tian Hao.

00:52:17.440 --> 00:52:18.170
I don't know.

00:52:20.190 --> 00:52:22.050
Are you still in contact with him?

00:52:22.360 --> 00:52:23.320
Do you know where he is?

00:52:23.320 --> 00:52:24.840
I've cut ties with him.

00:52:25.760 --> 00:52:26.760
Don't ask me about him,

00:52:26.760 --> 00:52:27.320
okay?

00:52:28.960 --> 00:52:30.420
My mentor's name is Ran Xi.

00:52:32.070 --> 00:52:33.200
Do you remember him?

00:52:33.840 --> 00:52:34.840
I used to work at

00:52:34.960 --> 00:52:36.560
Nanhuaishu Police Station.

00:52:39.550 --> 00:52:40.750
I'm a police officer.

00:52:41.030 --> 00:52:41.760
If you're in danger,

00:52:41.760 --> 00:52:42.620
you can tell me.

00:52:42.920 --> 00:52:44.550
What danger could I possibly be in?

00:52:44.550 --> 00:52:46.000
That's good if there isn't any.

00:52:46.000 --> 00:52:47.360
I noticed you seemed nervous,

00:52:47.360 --> 00:52:48.710
constantly looking back.

00:52:48.710 --> 00:52:50.440
Are you in some kind of trouble?

00:53:03.710 --> 00:53:04.480
Do you know why I keep

00:53:04.480 --> 00:53:05.920
looking back when I walk?

00:53:08.230 --> 00:53:09.760
Back when I was in school,

00:53:10.840 --> 00:53:11.970
I was walking ahead,

00:53:13.510 --> 00:53:14.280
and when I got home,

00:53:14.280 --> 00:53:16.140
I found out he was right behind me.

00:53:16.880 --> 00:53:19.210
He followed me through the entire hutong,

00:53:20.360 --> 00:53:21.820
without making any sound,

00:53:22.880 --> 00:53:23.960
like a ghost.